    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简介</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team Rush冠军小队是一款足球竞技游戏，化身为可爱小猫，在绿茵场上奔跑破门！无论是否踢过足球，无论你有没有玩过足球游戏，在这里你都可以享受到足球的魅力，充分体验足球的快乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞争</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >球场的情况瞬息万变，在合适的时间做出正确的操作，帮助团队赢得顺利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/f6ef881c41e1d606057321de6e286307.poster.avif?t=1747746869\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/f6ef881c41e1d606057321de6e286307.webm?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/f6ef881c41e1d606057321de6e286307.mp4?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >队友是你永远可以信任的伙伴， 在对方进行逼抢时，和队友一同合作来摆脱困境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/3d4943b66c67f731a14d22c85894b5a8.poster.avif?t=1747746869\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/3d4943b66c67f731a14d22c85894b5a8.webm?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/3d4943b66c67f731a14d22c85894b5a8.mp4?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>观察</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款第一人称游戏中你需要时时刻刻观察队友和敌人的动向，否则就会丢失球权，错失进攻良机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/37dffcb35ac35214a16d97fc0f5d32c0.poster.avif?t=1747746869\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/37dffcb35ac35214a16d97fc0f5d32c0.webm?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086890/extras/37dffcb35ac35214a16d97fc0f5d32c0.mp4?t=1747746869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>目前，我们的服务器仅覆中国，盖美国东部、美国西部和欧洲中部地区。由于我们是来自中国的两人的小团队，对于其他地区的玩家，我们深感歉意。如果您所在的地区距离这些服务器位置较远，可能会遇到较高的网络延迟问题。我们承诺未来将逐步扩展至更多地区，以期为所有玩家提供更优质的服务。感谢您的理解与支持。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >问题反馈QQ群：310845838</p>",
